00:01:55.969 --> 00:01:58.969
They will build houses and live in them,

00:01:58.969 --> 00:02:02.969
and they will plant vineyards and eat their fruitage.

00:02:02.969 --> 00:02:04.969
They will not build for someone else to inhabit,

00:02:04.969 --> 00:02:07.969
nor will they plant for others to eat.

00:02:07.969 --> 00:02:11.969
For the days of my people will be like the days of a tree,

00:02:11.969 --> 00:02:13.969
and the work of their hands,

00:02:13.969 --> 00:02:18.969
my chosen ones will enjoy to the fall.

00:02:18.969 --> 00:02:20.969
Well done.

00:02:20.969 --> 00:02:25.969
Our sister spoke from the heart and breathed life into her material.

00:02:25.969 --> 00:02:30.969
It was evident in her tone of voice and facial expression.

00:02:30.969 --> 00:02:33.969
Of course, we need to be balanced.

00:02:33.969 --> 00:02:38.969
We could tire our listeners if we project a high level of enthusiasm

00:02:38.969 --> 00:02:41.969
throughout our presentation.

00:02:41.969 --> 00:02:47.969
To illustrate this, watch this brother giving a talk at the Kingdom Hall.

00:02:47.969 --> 00:02:51.969
What prophetic events can we expect in the near future?

00:02:51.969 --> 00:02:55.969
First, there will be a pronouncement of peace and security.

00:02:55.969 --> 00:02:59.969
Then, the great tribulation will begin when the nations turn on,

00:02:59.969 --> 00:03:02.969
babble on the great, the world empire of false religion.

00:03:02.969 --> 00:03:06.969
However, in harmony with the words of Matthew 24, 22,

00:03:06.969 --> 00:03:10.969
the attack will be cut short on account of the chosen ones.

00:03:10.969 --> 00:03:12.969
What will happen next?

00:03:12.969 --> 00:03:16.969
Gog of Megag, a coalition of nations will attack God's people.

00:03:16.969 --> 00:03:20.969
Also, what do you think?

00:03:20.969 --> 00:03:24.969
The speaker was clearly enthusiastic,

00:03:24.969 --> 00:03:29.969
a bit too enthusiastic about the devastating events to come.

00:03:29.969 --> 00:03:37.969
Also, our listeners will be distracted if we use the same gesture repeatedly.

00:03:37.969 --> 00:03:41.969
So we should try to make our gestures meaningful

00:03:41.969 --> 00:03:46.969
and show enthusiasm primarily when teaching main points

00:03:46.969 --> 00:03:50.969
and when motivating our listeners to action.

00:03:50.969 --> 00:03:53.969
