00:04:30.970 --> 00:04:33.970
the war of the great day of God, the Almighty.

00:04:33.970 --> 00:04:37.970
So, what must we do now?

00:04:37.970 --> 00:04:44.970
Romans 12-11 commands us to be a glow with this spirit.

00:04:44.970 --> 00:04:47.970
By putting enthusiasm into our delivery,

00:04:47.970 --> 00:04:51.970
we'll stimulate and motivate our listeners to action.
